 <div id="content">
<h2>background</h2>
    </div>

             <div id="col1" >

Capital Hill Consulting is an experienced consulting firm that can establish
sound management, information and government strategies for your business or
industry.

<br /><br />

We draw on two decades of senior management experience including successful
senior government positions, political campaigns, cooperative research
management and effective information technology project management.

<br /><br />

This century sees a world that needs maximum access to information.
Capital Hill Consulting can develop your information management strategy to
ensure that you are getting the right information to the right place at the
right time. In the information age, the application of information to influence
key decisions or link to networks will be crucial to maintaining your
competitive position.

<br /><br />

If you have a contribution to make on a national or industry level and want to
communicate your message to government or investors, Capital Hill Consulting
has the experience and skills that make the difference.


